### **4. 32_RealtimeChartPanel**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes real-time data as a smooth, live-updating chart using Matplotlib.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealtimeChartPanel - Live Data Visualization Tool

RealtimeChartPanel streams incoming values and displays them as a scrolling line chart.

## Features
- Clean animated charts  
- Adjustable update speed  
- Easy to adapt for sensors or simulations  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_RealtimeChartPanel.git
cd 32_RealtimeChartPanel
python visualize.py
